quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,Kul uhÄḟye ileyye ennehustemeÂṀa neferun minelcinni fekalu inna semÄḟÂṀna kurÂṀanen ÂṀaceben
  72,2,Yehdiy ilerruÅdi feamenna bihi ve len nuÅrike birabbina ehaden
  72,3,Ve ennehu teÂṀala ceddu rabbina mettehaze sahÄḟbeten ve la veleden
  72,4,Ve ennehu kane yekulu sefiyhuna ÂṀalellahi Åetatatan
  72,5,Ve enna zanenna en len tekulenÂṀinsu velcinnu ÂṀalellahi keziben
  72,6,Ve ennehu kane ricalun minelÂṀinsi yeÂṀuzune biricalin minelcinni fezaduhum rehekan
  72,7,Ve ennehum zannu kema zanentum en len yebÂṀasallahu ehaden
  72,8,Ve enna lemesnessemae fevecednaha muliet haresen Åediyden ve Åuhuben
  72,9,Ve enna kunna nakÂṀudu minha mekaÂṀÄḟde lissemÂṀÄḟ femen yestemiÂṀÄḟlÂṀane yecid lehu Åihahaben resaden
  72,10,Ve enna la nedriy eÅerrun uriyde bimen fiylÂṀardÄḟ em erade bihim rabbuhum reÅeden
  72,11,Ve enna minnessalihune ve minna dune zalike kunna taraika kÄḟdeden
  72,12,Ve enna zanenna en len nuÂṀcizallahe fiylÂṀardÄḟ ve len nuÂṀcizehu hereben
  72,13,Ve enna lema semiÂṀnelhuda amenna bihi femen yuÂṀmin birabbihi fela yehafu bahsen ve la rehekan
  72,14,Ve enna minnelmuslimune ve minnelkasitune femen esleme feulaike teharrev reÅeden
  72,15,Ve emmelkasitune fekanu licehenneme hataben
  72,16,Ve en levistekamu ÂṀalettariykati leeskaynahum maen Äadekan
  72,17,Lineftinehum fiyhi ve men yuÂṀrÄḟd ÂṀan zikri rabbihi yeslukhu ÂṀazaben saÂṀaden
  72,18,Ve ennelmesacide lillahi fela tedÂṀu maÂṀallahi ehaden
  72,19,Ve ennehu lemma kame ÂṀabdullahi yedÂṀuhu kadu yekunune ÂṀaleyhi libeden
  72,20,Kul innema edÂṀu rabbiy ve la uÅriku bihi ehaden
  72,21,Kul inniy la emliku lekum darran ve la reÅeden
  72,22,Kul inniy len yuciyreniy minallahi ehadun ve len ecide min dunihi multehaden
  72,23,ÄḞlla belaÄan minallahi ve risalatihi ve men yaÂṀsÄḟllahe ve resulehu feinne lehu nare cehenneme halidiyne fiyha ebeden
  72,24,Hatta iza reev ma yuÂṀadune feseyaÂṀlemune men edÂṀafu nasÄḟren ve ekallu ÂṀadeden
  72,25,Kul in edriy ekariybun ma tuÂṀadune em yecÂṀalu lehu rabbiy emeden
  72,26,ÂṀAlmulÄaybi fela yuzhiru ÂṀala Äaybihi ehaden
  72,27,ÄḞlla menirteda min resulin feinnehu yesluku min beyni yedeyhi ve min halfihi resaden
  72,28,LiyaÂṀleme en kad ebleÄu risalati rabbihim ve ehata bima lediyhim ve ahsa kulle ÅeyÂṀin ÂṀadeden